events :  
in javascript events are special functions  to trigger some control functionality.
  1. click
  2. double click
  3. mouseover
  4. mouseout 
  5. focus 
  6. blur 
  7. mousemove
  8. keyup
  9. keypress

note : in javascript every event is executing  from a method called 
   addEventListener 

button = id(btn) :
document.getElementById("btn").addEventListerner("click",Myfun)
  function Myfun()
  {
  alert("button clicked")
  }





